item.title: Trouble Loading MoparScape
item.dc:creator: @JxS JxS
item.description:
@JxS wrote:

Somethings fucked with your cache, try going to c:\windows and deleting the folder named “.mpr_file_store_32” and then re-running the client so it redownloads the cache.

And also, how long has this been happening? Or is it your first time with the client?
